Feature: Simple authentication
  In order to use the application
  As a registered user
  I can log in

  Scenario: I'm a registered user with correct password
    Given I access the url "/dashboard/"
    And I fill in "id_username" with "reg_user"
    When I fill in "id_password" with "reg_password"
    And I press "post_login_btn"
    Then I should be at url "/dashboard/"
    And I should see an element with id of "bt_user"

